00:13:26,700 --> 00:13:28,500
Let's continue class.

279
00:13:28,500 --> 00:13:31,170
Here, section four...

280
00:13:32,300 --> 00:13:34,200
Pull your shoulders back a little.

281
00:13:40,300 --> 00:13:42,220
How is Da Ke doing?

282
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,800
Listen up, everyone!

283
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:50,400
From now on,

284
00:13:50,400 --> 00:13:51,999
Xia Yu Hao is our new teammate.

285
00:13:51,999 --> 00:13:54,400
Please clap for him.

286
00:13:54,400 --> 00:13:56,000
Welcome. Welcome.

287
00:13:58,600 --> 00:14:00,400
What's going on?

288
00:14:03,100 --> 00:14:06,000
No one can resist volleyball's charm.

289
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:07,800
How come you came?

290
00:14:11,800 --> 00:14:12,600
All right, everyone,

291
00:14:12,601 --> 00:14:14,541
let's get on with practice.

292
00:14:14,541 --> 00:14:16,300
I'm not practicing.

293
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:20,000
Hello.

294
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:23,000
Zi Xuan, take Yu Hao to the commune to change into sports attire.

295
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:27,500
What is this?

296
00:14:29,300 --> 00:14:30,399
Who wants this?

297
00:14:30,400 --> 00:14:31,001
Exactly.

298
00:14:31,001 --> 00:14:34,700
Hey, don't think you're great just because the Coach asked you to join.

299
00:14:34,700 --> 00:14:38,800
Why are you being so arrogant when you don't even know how to serve?

300
00:14:38,800 --> 00:14:41,199
What does it have to do with you, short legs?

301
00:14:41,199 --> 00:14:42,700
You know how to fight?

302
00:14:42,700 --> 00:14:44,000
Who doesn't know how to fight?

303
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,401
Come at me then!

304
00:14:45,401 --> 00:14:47,500
- Jia Jun!
- You want to fight, is that it?

305
00:14:48,400 --> 00:14:50,000
You can't do that!

306
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,300
Senior.

307
00:14:55,300 --> 00:14:58,100
If you want to stay on the team, then don't fight.

308
00:14:58,100 --> 00:14:59,300
Wait a minute.

309
00:14:59,300 --> 00:15:01,300
Did you know we get suspended from the games if we fight,

310
00:15:01,300 --> 00:15:02,676
so you said all that?

311
00:15:02,676 --> 00:15:03,900
So what if that's true?

312
00:15:03,900 --> 00:15:06,500
Wow, you're too cunning.

313
00:15:06,500 --> 00:15:09,960
Aren't we just a bunch of innocent and kind high school students?

314
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:11,900
You guys threatened my grades just to force me to join this team.

315
00:15:11,900 --> 00:15:13,200
Do you think that's honorable?

316
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:14,101
That's right.

317
00:15:14,101 --> 00:15:17,800
I'm here now, so you can tell the Coach that.

318
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:19,100
Forcing him won't work. I'll go talk to the coach.

319
00:15:19,100 --> 00:15:21,200
Wait. Hold on. Hold on.

320
00:15:22,300 --> 00:15:24,200
How about this?

321
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:26,000
Pick one of us to serve.

322
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:28,100
If you can catch just one out of the three serves,

323
00:15:28,100 --> 00:15:31,320
then you don't have to practice. What about it?

324
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:33,400
Bring it on.

325
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:34,700
All right.

326
00:15:34,700 --> 00:15:36,201
Senior, let me do it!

327
00:15:36,201 --> 00:15:38,000
You're done for!

328
00:15:40,400 --> 00:15:41,800
I pick you.

329
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:45,400
I want to catch your serves.

330
00:15:47,200 --> 00:15:49,200
He's the manager of our team.

331
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:51,600
I know that, so what?

332
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:53,900
I just want to catch your serves.

333
00:15:55,300 --> 00:15:57,200
Do you dare?

334
00:16:05,100 --> 00:16:09,500
Start practice. Start with fast breaks.

335
00:16:09,500 --> 00:16:12,400
Aren't all ball teams like this?

336
00:16:12,400 --> 00:16:14,600
You don't have any guts?

337
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:19,400
You're such a coward.

338
00:16:19,400 --> 00:16:20,601
Don't be too much!

339
00:16:20,601 --> 00:16:21,500
Didn't I just tell you? He's our manager.

340
00:16:21,500 --> 00:16:24,300
Be more polite. Be more polite.

341
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:30,600
What if you lose?

342
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:32,600
Then I'll do anything you want.

343
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:51,400
Xuan...

344
00:16:51,400 --> 00:16:52,300
I know.

345
00:16:52,300 --> 00:16:55,260
I haven't watched Senior play in a long time.

346
00:16:55,260 --> 00:16:57,400
This is going to be good.

347
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:01,300
Let's do it.

348
00:17:02,300 --> 00:17:04,000
First ball!

349
00:17:10,200 --> 00:17:12,700
That was so easy, so easy!

350
00:17:13,700 --> 00:17:15,400
He's really strong.

351
00:17:18,700 --> 00:17:20,800
This is going to be 3-0.

352
00:17:20,800 --> 00:17:22,800
Second ball!

353
00:17:28,800 --> 00:17:29,800
This is the first time

354
00:17:29,800 --> 00:17:32,800
I've seen someone get used to Senior Zi Xuan's serves so fast.

355
00:17:32,800 --> 00:17:35,499
The next serve will determine the score. It's the ace serve.

356
00:17:35,500 --> 00:17:36,500
Xuan.

357
00:17:36,501 --> 00:17:39,199
But I think he's more agile than you.

358
00:17:39,200 --> 00:17:40,900
What did you say?

359
00:17:45,700 --> 00:17:48,000
Step back. Everyone step back.

360
00:17:50,500 --> 00:17:52,400
It's going to be a jump serve.

361
00:18:07,300 --> 00:18:08,699
Nice one.

362
00:18:08,700 --> 00:18:10,500
That was really fierce.

363
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:12,500
Senior!

364
00:18:12,500 --> 00:18:13,400
- Are you okay?
-Zi Xuan!

365
00:18:13,400 --> 00:18:15,000
I'm fine.

366
00:18:18,600 --> 00:18:20,620
What else do you have to say?

367
00:18:24,800 --> 00:18:27,100
Stop forcing yourself.

368
00:18:27,100 --> 00:18:28,700
Let's go.

369
00:18:42,900 --> 00:18:43,500
It's really hot, right?

370
00:18:43,500 --> 00:18:45,000
Yes.

371
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:46,100
This is your punishment.

372
00:18:46,100 --> 00:18:48,820
You actually really jumped?

373
00:18:48,820 --> 00:18:50,500
I accidentally become too serious.

374
00:18:50,500 --> 00:18:52,600
Don't be angry.

375
00:18:55,700 --> 00:18:57,200
Hey.

376
00:18:57,200 --> 00:18:59,300
Are you sure you want him on the team?

377
00:18:59,300 --> 00:19:02,000
He will ruin the team spirit.

378
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,100
We don't have a choice.

379
00:19:05,100 --> 00:19:07,100
Our team is really lacking a strong spiker

380
00:19:07,100 --> 00:19:09,000
and he really has the potential.

381
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:10,400
So what if he has potential?

382
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:13,000
His attitude sucks, so he's useless.

383
00:19:14,300 --> 00:19:16,700
How about we do it like the old times?

384
00:19:16,700 --> 00:19:18,800
I'll take care of his attitude.

385
00:19:18,800 --> 00:19:21,000
The training, I'll leave to you.

386
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:22,600
That again?

387
00:19:22,600 --> 00:19:23,800
Please.

388
00:19:23,800 --> 00:19:24,400
No.

389
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:25,800
- Please.
- No.

390
00:19:25,800 --> 00:19:27,400
I'm begging you.

391
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:29,700
I won't get up if you don't agree.

392
00:19:29,700 --> 00:19:31,800
Okay... Fine.

393
00:19:32,700 --> 00:19:34,600
Promise me?

394
00:19:34,600 --> 00:19:35,900
You're so annoying.

395
00:19:35,900 --> 00:19:37,500
Here, here, here. Let me do it.

396
00:19:37,500 --> 00:19:39,400
Relax. Relax.

397
00:19:40,500 --> 00:19:42,400
Master, doesn't this feel comfortable?

398
00:19:42,400 --> 00:19:44,300
Comfortable, my ass.

399
00:19:45,300 --> 00:19:47,400
Don't do that again.

400
00:19:47,400 --> 00:19:49,300
Okay.

401
00:19:50,100 --> 00:19:52,280
Does this reach the bottom of your knee?

402
00:19:52,280 --> 00:19:54,200
More on this side.

403
00:20:00,700 --> 00:20:03,600
Are you really joining the team?

404
00:20:03,600 --> 00:20:05,600
He Zhong Zhong is threatening me with my grades,

405
00:20:05,600 --> 00:20:07,600
how can I not go?

406
00:20:07,600 --> 00:20:09,900
You're right.

407
00:20:09,900 --> 00:20:12,700
Here, eat this.

408
00:20:12,700 --> 00:20:14,600
We're eating soon.

409
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:17,600
What about me?

410
00:20:17,600 --> 00:20:20,200
Xia Yu Hao!

411
00:20:20,200 --> 00:20:22,300
Do you remember me?

412
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:25,200
Who are you?

413
00:20:25,200 --> 00:20:26,500
Hi.

414
00:20:27,600 --> 00:20:28,900
Hi.

415
00:20:32,700 --> 00:20:34,900
They are all afraid of Xia Yu Hao.

416
00:20:34,900 --> 00:20:37,600
Even though you only just transferred, they are still scared of you.

417
00:20:37,600 --> 00:20:41,500
I'd say they know things well; at least, they know who not to mess with.

418
00:20:41,500 --> 00:20:43,700
Xia Yu Hao,

419
00:20:43,700 --> 00:20:45,600
you don't need to be too courteous with me.

420
00:20:45,600 --> 00:20:48,399
You got expelled because of me.

421
00:20:48,399 --> 00:20:52,200
So it's not a big deal treating you to this meal.

422
00:20:52,200 --> 00:20:54,420
He was the one who wanted to help you.

423
00:20:56,300 --> 00:20:58,800
I was just in it for the fight.

424
00:20:58,800 --> 00:21:01,500
But you're the one who fought them off.

425
00:21:01,500 --> 00:21:04,000
In the end, you're still the one who saved me.

426
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:06,500
Whatever. I need to go now.

427
00:21:06,500 --> 00:21:10,900
Hey, just let her finish talking first.

428
00:21:10,900 --> 00:21:13,500
Can't we still be friends?

429
00:21:13,500 --> 00:21:16,600
I don't have many friends.

430
00:21:16,600 --> 00:21:18,900
How would a pretty girl not have friends?

431
00:21:18,900 --> 00:21:22,800
Yes, I'm always alone.

432
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:27,000
Do you have some kind of a problem?

433
00:21:27,000 --> 00:21:28,799
Do you insult people too much? Gossip too much?

434
00:21:28,800 --> 00:21:31,100
Boyfriend snatcher?

435
00:21:31,100 --> 00:21:33,700
How can you say that?

436
00:21:35,600 --> 00:21:37,299
Then why would a pretty girl have no friends?

437
00:21:37,299 --> 00:21:39,300
Are you dumb?

438
00:21:39,300 --> 00:21:40,976
He has a brain that is different from others.

439
00:21:40,976 --> 00:21:43,020
Don't take it too seriously.

440
00:21:44,600 --> 00:21:47,540
How did you know that my brain's different from the others?

441
00:21:47,540 --> 00:21:49,800
Don't say anything stupid.

442
00:21:52,700 --> 00:21:54,900
Hey, I really need to go now.

443
00:21:54,900 --> 00:21:57,000
Wait for me.

444
00:21:58,400 --> 00:21:59,700
Hey. Hey!

445
00:21:59,700 --> 00:22:02,800
I'm not done talking yet!

446
00:22:09,500 --> 00:22:12,200
What time do you think it is right now?

447
00:22:13,400 --> 00:22:16,300
All right, I know.

448
00:22:17,300 --> 00:22:19,400
Stinky Zi Xuan.

449
00:22:24,700 --> 00:22:26,199
Watch your footsteps.

450
00:22:26,200 --> 00:22:28,000
Yes, Senior!

451
00:22:28,800 --> 00:22:30,300
Jump higher.

452
00:22:30,300 --> 00:22:31,900
Yes, Senior!

453
00:22:33,100 --> 00:22:35,200
Hey, your posture is off.

454
00:22:35,200 --> 00:22:36,800
Yes, Senior.

455
00:22:37,700 --> 00:22:38,800
Good shot!

456
00:22:38,800 --> 00:22:41,399
Zi Xuan, I looked in the classroom,

457
00:22:41,399 --> 00:22:43,000
but Xia Yu Hao wasn't there either.

458
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:45,600
I called him many times too, but he's not answering.

459
00:22:45,600 --> 00:22:48,800
What do we do now? He still has so much training to do.

460
00:22:50,000 --> 00:22:51,940
I'll go find him. I'll leave this to you.

461
00:22:51,940 --> 00:22:54,000
Listen up!

462
00:22:54,000 --> 00:22:55,980
Xiao Xiao is in charge now.

463
00:22:55,980 --> 00:22:57,700
- Yes, Senior!
- Yes, Senior!

464
00:22:58,500 --> 00:23:00,700
Hurry, hurry up and practice!

465
00:23:00,700 --> 00:23:02,000
- Yes.
- Yes.

466
00:23:15,700 --> 00:23:16,600
Junior,

467
00:23:16,601 --> 00:23:19,100
do you know where Xia Yu Hao is?

468
00:23:19,100 --> 00:23:21,700
A good student like you wouldn't dare go to those places.

469
00:23:21,700 --> 00:23:22,800
Hey.

470
00:23:22,800 --> 00:23:26,000
Do you want me to get Ms. Zhong Zhong to come and ask you?

471
00:23:26,000 --> 00:23:28,000
What's the matter?

472
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:31,000
Come on, I'll take you there.

473
00:23:42,400 --> 00:23:44,700
Hey, are we there yet?

474
00:23:44,700 --> 00:23:46,800
It's nearby.

475
00:23:50,300 --> 00:23:53,000
Hey, where exactly is he?

476
00:23:56,900 --> 00:23:59,600
It's the second shop, the X Club.

477
00:24:01,900 --> 00:24:03,700
You're not coming in with me?

478
00:24:04,900 --> 00:24:06,600
Didn't you want to go find him on your own?

479
00:24:06,600 --> 00:24:08,700
Go on your own then.

480
00:24:08,700 --> 00:24:09,801
Bye.

481
00:24:09,801 --> 00:24:11,900
Hey, Wang Zhen Wen.

482
00:24:11,900 --> 00:24:13,000
Hey!

483
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:23,800
What are you doing?

484
00:24:27,400 --> 00:24:29,300
You can't do drugs here.

485
00:24:29,300 --> 00:24:31,600
What does that have to do with you?

486
00:24:31,600 --> 00:24:33,500
What did you say?

487
00:24:34,400 --> 00:24:36,700
Please leave.

488
00:24:38,100 --> 00:24:39,700
What?

489
00:24:39,700 --> 00:24:41,300
Xia Yu Hao!

490
00:24:41,300 --> 00:24:42,500
Xia Yu Hao!

491
00:24:42,500 --> 00:24:43,300
What are you doing?

492
00:24:43,300 --> 00:24:44,300
Why did you come here?

493
00:24:44,300 --> 00:24:46,000
Go away!

494
00:24:48,700 --> 00:24:50,300
Go away!

495
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:53,500
Go away!

496
00:24:53,500 --> 00:24:55,500
Let's go!

497
00:25:03,600 --> 00:25:04,700
What are you guys doing?

498
00:25:04,700 --> 00:25:07,000
If you don't leave, I'm calling the police!

499
00:25:24,500 --> 00:25:26,376
You don't even know how to fight so why did you join in?

500
00:25:26,376 --> 00:25:29,000
Take this. Put it on yourself.

501
00:25:38,200 --> 00:25:40,600
Does your family know you're working here?

502
00:25:40,600 --> 00:25:42,000
What does that have to do with you?

503
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:44,200
Look after yourself first.

504
00:25:49,700 --> 00:25:51,600
Is your leg okay?

505
00:25:57,700 --> 00:25:58,799
I'm leaving first.

506
00:25:58,799 --> 00:26:00,200
Hey.

507
00:26:03,800 --> 00:26:05,100
This--

508
00:26:08,800 --> 00:26:10,000
You're hurt so badly

509
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:11,920
and you still say you're fine?

510
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:24,000
You're actually not a bad person, so why pretend?

511
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:25,399
Pretend what?

512
00:26:25,399 --> 00:26:27,200
Did I ever say I was a bad person?

513
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:30,220
Do bad people ever admit they're bad?

514
00:26:35,400 --> 00:26:38,000
Why did you cover for me?

515
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:40,600
The manager has to protect his teammates,

516
00:26:42,100 --> 00:26:43,900
or should I have let you take the hit?

517
00:26:43,900 --> 00:26:46,600
Did you think you wouldn't get hurt yourself?

518
00:26:46,600 --> 00:26:48,600
Anyway, I can't get on the court and play.

519
00:26:48,600 --> 00:26:50,780
So it doesn't make any difference to me.

520
00:26:57,700 --> 00:27:00,000
Let me take you home later.

521
00:27:01,100 --> 00:27:02,500
Thanks.

522
00:27:38,200 --> 00:27:40,300
Does it still hurt?

523
00:27:40,300 --> 00:27:41,940
It's all right.

524
00:27:46,700 --> 00:27:47,999
Hey, let me say this first though.

525
00:27:47,999 --> 00:27:49,699
I won't be good and just show up to practice

526
00:27:49,699 --> 00:27:51,720
because you blocked them for me earlier.

527
00:27:53,700 --> 00:27:55,400
My house is here.

528
00:27:57,900 --> 00:27:59,800
I won't use this as an exchange.

529
00:27:59,800 --> 00:28:02,560
You can't be a good player if you're not playing with your heart.

530
00:28:02,560 --> 00:28:03,800
Since you're so reluctant like this,

531
00:28:03,800 --> 00:28:05,000
I'll talk to Coach tomorrow

532
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:06,800
and get her permission to excuse you from the team.

533
00:28:06,800 --> 00:28:08,400
Thanks for walking me home.

534
00:28:08,400 --> 00:28:09,800
Hey!

535
00:28:09,800 --> 00:28:11,600
Is it some kind of a joke to you?

536
00:28:11,600 --> 00:28:12,899
Threatening my grades to force me to join the team.

537
00:28:12,899 --> 00:28:14,700
Turning my life upside down

538
00:28:14,700 --> 00:28:16,800
and now you're saying it's over just like that.

539
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:20,300
Why are you getting mad?

540
00:28:20,300 --> 00:28:21,500
I...

541
00:28:22,600 --> 00:28:24,600
You didn't want to join the team, right?

542
00:28:24,600 --> 00:28:25,800
Yes, I didn't want to.

543
00:28:25,800 --> 00:28:27,300
A team like yours has no future,

544
00:28:27,300 --> 00:28:29,240
so I don't want to practice on it.

545
00:28:33,700 --> 00:28:35,800
We were in the top eight in the High School League last year.

546
00:28:35,800 --> 00:28:37,999
This year, we'll definitely make it to the top four.

547
00:28:37,999 --> 00:28:41,000
Everyone is working hard for this goal.

548
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:44,900
This is also the last opportunity for He Cheng En and myself.

549
00:28:44,900 --> 00:28:48,400
If you don't get it, then forget it.

550
00:28:48,400 --> 00:28:50,200
Also,

551
00:28:50,200 --> 00:28:51,700
I won't tell anyone where you're working as a part-timer.

552
00:28:51,700 --> 00:28:53,300
Good night.

553
00:28:54,400 --> 00:28:56,200
Hey, you--

554
00:29:54,600 --> 00:29:57,300
Do you only know how to solve problems through fighting?

555
00:29:59,200 --> 00:30:00,300
What's so fun about this?

